{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I understand that this-- when I used to go with my father to listen to in the synagogue, to listen to what was going on, what's going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I said to some people, some friends I know here in America, that we did not imagine that bad like that could happen.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We know there are discriminations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There are demonstrations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't let any people go into the stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this was only till 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew, for example, about the, the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew-- we demonstrated on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are getting the Germans [INAUDIBLE] again the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we figured that the Jewish people in Germany were only a quarter percent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The majority of them had opportunity to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is the way by us-- we were 10% of the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Poland, they was more magnanimous to the Jews because we were a big part of the population.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we were-- we did not feel the, the, the, the tragedy that was going on in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason was, because when the tragedies actually happened later on, the Russians occupied our hometown in 1939.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then all the news from Germany-- derogatory against Germany-- stopped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cut off from Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, for example, the, the, the, the, the Russians were gloating with happiness that the Germans are destroying so many ships in England.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans are doing so many [? tonnage ?] to the Germans, and the Germans are doing so-- because, if you recall, when the Germans-- when the Russians came into my hometown, they had a pact, a secret pact between the Russians and the Germans.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the River Bug, which divided part of the area where the Russians occupied, became Vistula, Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They renamed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
